                                "stop": 11.111,
                                "byte_start": 86882,
                                "byte_stop": 131395,
                                "text": "The Opinion of the Court in number 93-714 U.S. Bancorp Mortgage Company v. Bonner Mall will be announced by Justice Scalia."
